+## Court Decision
+
+File explorer implementation status: `NOT_PRESENT_IN_SOURCES`
+
+Recommended next safe step: create a new v0.dev/shadcn UI file explorer design for `pala-os-v5`, then adapt it into v5 through the existing evidence/report gate.
+
+Allowed reuse:
